<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00">今天<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是萬聖節了喔～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我太期待<delay8 />這一天的到來，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />心臟都興奮到快跳出來了！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />先拿好糖果～<delay20 />然後穿上那件衣服～<delay20 />
然後、然後<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay20 />準備齊全了！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於到<delay8 />萬聖節當天了～！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鬼怪們一定<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也很期待今天，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後開心地跑來玩<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃，<delay20 />討厭啦～！<delay20 />好可怕～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望不要有真正的鬼怪<delay20 />
跑來參加<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />夜晚快點來臨吧～！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家一起<delay8 />享受萬聖節，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後製造很多<delay8 />歡樂的回憶吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">馬上就到<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節的時間囉！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不給糖就搗蛋<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不曉得到時候能不能順利說出口呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為了今天<delay8 />
準備了特別的裝扮，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可要好好期待喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />活動差不多要正式開始了，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你沒有忘記帶什麼吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在萬聖節忘記帶東西<delay8 /><anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是攸關性命喔？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別是<delay20 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糖、<delay8 />果！<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是沒有這個，<delay20 />就會被其他人惡作劇喔！<delay frames="90" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我？<delay40 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我放在衣服的口袋裡<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯、<delay8 />嗯，<delay20 />有很多糖果喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay40 />
<colour id="4" />糟了～！<delay40 />這件衣服的口袋<delay20 />
不知道什麼時候破了一個洞～～！<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，<delay8 />我剛剛看到<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />
放著南瓜家具喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到南瓜，<delay8 />就會想到萬聖節！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個家具<delay20 />一定是<delay8 />
喜歡活動的人放的喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不覺得<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有種萬聖節的氛圍嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想這應該都是<delay8 />
多虧了幫忙裝飾的人吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太感謝那個人了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />到處都是南瓜家具，
多虧如此，<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在島上超有萬聖節氣氛的～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到這種情景，<delay20 />
我對活動當天的期待已經快爆發啦。<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />傷腦筋啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看你看，<delay20 />這座島<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是已經變成萬聖節的世界啦！？<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我能切身地感受到……<delay8 />
做這些裝飾的人對於萬聖節<delay8 />
那爆發般的熱情喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想其他島嶼的人<delay8 />看到這些，<delay8 />
一定會很驚訝的！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為這些真的很有氣氛，<delay8 />超棒的啊～！
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />好想趕快<delay8 />在進入萬聖節狀態的
<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay20 />
享受活動喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>